**How it works?** When i clone the blocklist site, i am the only maintainer of the site, others can not submit new sites. I can give my site private signing key to other people i trust so they can also update the site or delete existing entries. On the site i can invite the visitors to send me new URLs to block.

[Here i submit my blocklist](/1TaLkFrMwvbNsooF4ioKAY9EuxTBTjipT/?Topic:1530187949_1L4dZcDF2maSKHDy788yhxpYnBWnXadUtS/Pornography+sites+blocklist+by+ssdifnskdjfnsdjk). it will contain p0rn sites.

If you have ambitions to maintain public blocklist, you have to clone nofish's [sample site](/1FiLTerEAHp7UT8Aw2zQBypcm5T14kgZDa/) and then be manually editting filters/sites.json file to add new bad sites, sample file:

{
  "siteblocks": {
    "1LwVp13w4tXM9HTpJB3YQGvfVK9pUwKDHg": {
      "date_added": 1530012785,
      "name": "Sample blocked site",
      "reason": "Just a site on the blocklist"
    }**,**
    "1N**********aUc": {
      "date_added": 1530012785,
      "name": "Site name here",
      "reason": "Short description why it was blacklisted"
    }**,**
    "12**********PZe": {
      "date_added": 1530012785,
      "name": "Site name here",
      "reason": "Short description why it was blacklisted"
    }
  }
}

(note the comma after each site block, except the last one)

After editting, "Sign and publish" the site from its (0) menu and spread the word. Note that modifications in the index.html, js, css files will be lost once you Upgrade site (the button that can be found in the site's menu on ZeroHello wich adds new modifications made on the site from which you clonned). Blocking user is a serious tasks, and should be done with knowledge that all past and future content of this user will become invisible (until muting is disabled). So users should be careful and have good reasons to enable blocking of the long lists of users. Newly added users to the blocklist seems currently not being updated to the subscribers. User blocklist subscriber have to re-visit the site and disable+enable blocking again. Sites bocklist is good, newly added sites are automaticaly updated to subscribers.

